// ============================================================================
// RECRUITER OS FACADE — Single entry-point for all Recruiter OS backend calls
// Mirrors the aiMatchingFacade.jsw pattern: page code imports from ONE file
// so the Wix bundler doesn't choke on 40+ separate module imports.
// ============================================================================

// --- Core Recruiter Service ---
